GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
SESSION LAW 2025-14
HOUSE BILL 26
AN ACT TO DEANNEX CERTAIN DESCRIBED TERRITORIES AND MAKE OTHER
CHANGES TO VARIOUS LOCAL LAWS.
The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
PART I. TOWN OF MADISON SATELLITE ANNEXATION CAP REMOVAL
SECTION 1. G.S. 160A-58.1(b) reads as rewritten:
"(b) A noncontiguous area proposed for annexation must meet all of the following
standards:
…
